<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, minimum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no" />
  <meta name="apple-touch-fullscreen" content="yes" />
  <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes" />
  <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="black" />
  <meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no" />
  <title>马桶上的招聘节</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/matong.css?r=3333">
</head>
<body>
<div class="apply hidden">
  <span class="middle-helper">
        </span><div class="wrap middle-content">
  <header>
    <img src="images/mt-tt.png">
  </header>

  <section class="white-box">
    <img src="images/box.png" class="box-bg">

    <div class="box-con">

      <!--第一步-->
      <form action="xxxx/" id="progressFirst" method="post">
      <dl class="apply-progress">
        <dt class="pg"><span class="current">1</span><i></i><span>2</span><i></i><span>3</span></dt>
        <dd class="form-control">

          <p><label>姓名</label></p>
          <p><input type="text" data-msg="请输入姓名"></p>
          <p><label>您的职位</label></p>
          <p><input type="text" placeholder="最多8个字" maxlength="8" data-msg="请输入您的职位"></p>
          <p><label>您的公司简称</label></p>
          <p><input type="text" placeholder="最多6个字" maxlength="6" data-msg="请输入您的公司简称"></p>
          <p class="err hidden">输入错误消息区域</p>
          <p class="t-center"><a class="next" href="javascript:;">下一步</a></p>

        </dd>
      </dl>
      </form>

      <!--第二布-->
      <form action="xxxx/" id="progressSecond" method="post" class="none">
      <dl class="apply-progress">
        <dt class="pg"><span class="current">1</span><i class="current"></i><span class="current">2</span><i></i><span>3</span></dt>
        <dd class="form-control">

          <p><label>手机号</label></p>
          <p><input type="text" name="phone" data-msg="请输入手机号" maxlength="11"></p>
          <p><label>微信号</label></p>
          <p><input type="text" placeholder="最多8个字" maxlength="8" data-msg="请输入微信号" data-unnecessary="1"></p>
          <p class="err hidden">输入错误消息区域</p>
          <p class="t-center"><a class="next" href="javascript:;">下一步</a></p>
        </dd>
      </dl>
      </form>

      <!--最后一步-->
      <dl class="apply-progress none"  id="progressThird">
        <dt class="pg"><span class="current">1</span><i class="current"></i><span class="current">2</span><i class="current"></i><span class="current">3</span></dt>
        <dd class="form-control apply-end">
          <p><strong>最后一步</strong></p>
          <p>分享马桶招聘节到朋友圈 <br/>即可完成报名</p>
          <p class="t-center"><a class="next" href="javascript:;">立即分享</a></p>
        </dd>
      </dl>

      <!--报名成功-->
      <dl class="apply-progress apply-success none">
        <dt>报名成功</dt>
        <dd class="form-control">
          <p>
            1.请您尽快下载BOSS直聘 <br/>
            2.使用您报名的手机号 <em>18611224456</em><br/>
            注册BOSS直聘<br/>
            3.完善信息并发布至少一个职位<br/>
            4.在BOSS直聘里，分享我们为您准备好的微JD，微JD热度越高，活动当天排名越高
          </p>

          <p>3月24日 <br/>
            10000+牛人等您来抢 <br/>
            不见不散</p>
          <p class="t-center mt10"><a class="next" href="javascript:;">下载BOSS直聘</a></p>
        </dd>
      </dl>

    </div>
  </section>
</div>

  <p class="rule">活动规则</p>
</div>

<script src="js/lib/jquery-2.1.1.min.js"></script>
<script src="js/utils/validator.js"></script>
<script src="js/site/apply.js"></script>
</body>
</html>


